settings-privacy-secret-redaction-title = Secret redaction
settings-privacy-secret-redaction-description = When this setting is enabled, Warp will scan blocks, the contents of Warp Drive objects, and Oz prompts for potential sensitive information and prevent saving or sending this data to any servers. You can customize this list via regexes.
settings-privacy-custom-secret-redaction-title = Custom secret redaction
settings-privacy-custom-secret-redaction-description = Use regex to define additional secrets or data you'd like to redact. This will take effect when the next command runs. You can use the inline (?i) flag as a prefix to your regex to make it case-insensitive.
